OL,6,FCPOS staff are responsible for
OL,7,Fenforcement duties at stations, on
OL,8,Fbuses and checks on taxis, as well as
OL,9,Fanti- violence and aggression policing
OL,10,Facross the transport network often
OL,11,Fworking closely with the Metropolitan,
OL,12,FCity of London and British Transport
OL,13,FPolice.
