OL,6,FAdding the company is "refusing to
OL,7,Fdeal with pay parity issues with
OL,8,Fequivalent London Underground staff
OL,9,Fwho earn considerably more."
OL,11,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,12,Fsaid: "Our members keep London and its
OL,13,Fresidents safe and sound on the TfL
OL,14,Fnetwork.
